SessionedTextBox.htmlText:
Statistics on health care provision and spending by country,

as presented on the Bill Moyers & Co. website (http://billmoyers.com/2012/07/03/the-health-spending-map-of-the-world/) on July 3, 2012 and in the Guardian Newspaper's Data Blog on June 30. Source of the data is the World Health Organization, and most data was extracted for the year 2010.

It was trivial to enter the data into Weave for this visualization. All that was needed was to provide a complete set of IS0-3 country codes that corresponded to the world map already on our site.
